		"description": "<p>At 15th level, your psionic senses reach their apex. Your darkvision’s range increases by 30 feet and can penetrate magical darkness. The range of your blindsight from @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.JS4hJKjyRysllXjq]{Preternatural Awareness} increases to 90 feet, and you also gain Truesight with a range of 60 feet while it is active. You can also choose to cast @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.1sp8qzuofkjmunsd]{Arcane Eye} instead of @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.usz7we3sepg9tv9d]{Clairvoyance} (with the same modifications) when you use your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.rCOsk7xIuEs5BnXS]{Remote Viewing} feature.</p>",
